</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Bank fishing</strong> is productive in well-known access points like Hendricks Park.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Drift boats</strong> offer better reach and control, especially in wider sections like the lower McKenzie.
    </li>
</ul>
